{"tid":1466091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【拆局】藍絲式無敵文宣：有利嘅，因為自己；冇利嘅，因為敵人","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:59:59.000Z","uid":157304,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"87b8a353664fd8e81115f3f1687f39173632cc24","tid":1466091,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:31:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要學識藍絲嘅超強團結同煽情</span><br />\n<br />\n先聽日嘅情況，再做文宣<br />\n如果冇人鬧：咪話自己捉到公安同黑社會，以武制暴成功<br />\n如果被人鬧：係鬼搞事先，黑警借勢攻機場，喝記者，抗爭者以武制暴，為以往受傷被捕嘅人討回公道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">總之點都唔撚指責同分化<br />\n將任何素材變成有利自己</span></span>"},{"pid":"34ca2e0e5bc4123e8a451e83a4beddb3370ecb58","tid":1466091,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:32:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係鬼嘅連登仔，即刻一人一post叫人冷靜！不指責！不分化！</span>"},{"pid":"d48ce3cb93117274e97e522a9f1959ade3b04f61","tid":1466091,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:35:32.000Z","msg":"藍絲 真係無動搖 <br />\n抵死 邊個叫你出來 打死佢地就啱"},{"pid":"e8c32983fac97ff7191fd42a6004a38416da1b6f","tid":1466091,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣記住用呢個素材！<br />\n示威者全部係還手！</span><br />\n<br />\n[正視聽]黑警舉真槍前因後果<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1465260/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1465260/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5167c7ae17b6f642a91408c500a85d4dc9ac5ec8","tid":1466091,"uid":260793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b598130e16c1a1e8013da411d038f900ab7971d8","tid":1466091,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8c32983fac97ff7191fd42a6004a38416da1b6f","tid":1466091,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201